  "detailed_description": "<h1>From Keep Games</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Produce your soldiers, upgrade your equipment, and fight to win in a chaotic castle!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your team for 1-4 Online Co-op and PVE mode options! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determine your strategy and be the first to destroy the opposing tower. As the commander, create a strategy for your team, determine soldier production, and provide support on the battlefield! As the blacksmith, create weapons , as the armor master, create armor, and as the engineer, develop the castle, and manage your economy. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE/LOCAL MULTIPLAYER MADNESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To win in online multiplayer mode, you will need to work together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/6ee77aa9dff4f58fc2655e47fae7692c.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Sabotage your friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infuriate your friend by slapping them during the production phase when tensions are high!!!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/39c738185028661094938d0d9a03fafd.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Basic Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick production within the tower is very important; move with WASD and interact with items using O and P.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay attention to upgrades, and be stronger than your opponent; you must keep a balance between your resource development and production objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can create a different strategy in each game; runes determine your game strategy, move as a team and steer your game strategy with your runes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/815d6a33844fb82ab4fd4789aa9baabf.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/1487f6ff14795026b9d7003b11330a5f.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the Commander, you determine the production. Analyze the enemies coming from the opposing tower and determine your production order well!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are the opponents too close? Attack them with the defense weapons on the tower!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does your army need support? Go to the battlefield and give them power!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/eb16c5421a9249fee4bafb7ba5d152df.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/ba851b05515b2f7b749afe4ee25b4345.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an Engineer, you determine upgrades. Speeding up production and improving the raw materials will help you produce soldiers faster and make them stronger!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to support the production within the tower. Train horses for the cavalry, produce shields for the infantry!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Siege weapons are under your control. Don't forget to research the trebuchet to capture the enemy tower!</p></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/681d3e596f293df98d8140e5e765444d.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/cff457bbda41bab894970b21cc01e6a1.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Blacksmith role, you will produce weapons for your soldiers. Swords for infantry, crossbows for archers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Melt the raw materials, pour it into a sword mold, cool it down and sharpen it with an anvil. The weapons are ready for battle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to get your soldiers out of the tower faster, you should coordinate with the armor master and quickly complete the production.</p></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/c237d7fe1de69cc032aa53be79647c36.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=141 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/87cd0bbdf3cd0a038040c3b872ad475b.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the role of armorer, you will produce armor for your soldiers. All soldiers want armor!!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Melt the raw materials, pour it into an armor mold, cool it down and strengthen it with an anvil. Your soldiers are ready to go!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to get your soldiers out of the tower faster, you should coordinate with the blacksmith and complete the production quickly.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Send your wrongly produced or dressed soldier into the void!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.poster.avif?t=1761055403\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.webm?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317820/extras/d922cde9e573b952b6f2739de47c92dc.mp4?t=1761055403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
